OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCBI settles legal action   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbrought by sacked boss     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The CBI business group has settled     
OL,6, legal action brought by its former boss
OL,7, Tony Danker for wrongful dismissal.    
OL,9,FMr Danker was sacked with immediate    
OL,10,Feffect in 2023 following complaints    
OL,11,Fabout his behaviour.                   
OL,13,FHis exit came as other separate        
OL,14,Fallegations of historical misconduct at
OL,15,Fthe lobby group were uncovered but were
OL,16,Funconnected to Mr Danker.              
OL,18,FThe CBI confirmed it had agreed an     
OL,19,F"undisclosed settlement" with its      
OL,20,Fformer director-general.               
